00550         public
00551         Rational
00552         Add(
00553             Rational rational
00554             )
00555         {
00556             if(denominator.Equals(rational.denominator))
00557             {
00558                 return new Rational(
00559                     numerator + rational.numerator,
00560                     denominator.Clone()
00561                     );
00562             }
00563 
00564             Polynomial num = numerator * rational.denominator + rational.numerator * denominator;
00565             Polynomial denom = denominator * rational.denominator;
00566             return new Rational(num, denom);
00567         }
